<!-- About company -->
<section class="container pb-5 mb-md-2 mb-lg-4">
  <h1 class="border-bottom pb-4">About Us</h1>
  <div class="row pt-2 pt-md-3 gy-4 py-xl-3">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <p class="fs-lg pe-lg-4 mb-1 mb-lg-4">
        We believe that cutting-edge technology and custom software should be accessible to everyone, not just big tech
        companies, large corporations, or startups with millions in seed funding. Our engineers and developers have
        backgrounds working for these major tech companies and use the same technologies employed by industry leaders
        like
        Square, Apple, Netflix, Basecamp, and Jobber, to name a few. Rather than contributing to the growth of big
        corporations,
        we apply our skills and industry expertise to the benefit of your business or startup.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <%= image_tag "industries/04.jpg", class: "rounded-3", alt: "Industry" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container pb-5 mb-md-2 mb-lg-4">
  <h1 class="border-bottom pb-4">Our Mission</h1>
  <div class="row pt-2 pt-md-3 gy-4 py-xl-3">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <%= image_tag "industries/05.jpg", class: "rounded-3", alt: "Industry" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <p class="fs-lg ps-lg-4 mb-1 mb-lg-4">
        Our mission is to close the gap in access to advanced technology and custom software for small businesses and
        startups, regardless of industry. From small local service businesses looking to grow, or artisanal bakers
        delivery the best pies in town, we're on your side.
        <br>
        We understand that smaller entities face significant challenges in acquiring the resources
        and expertise necessary to compete with larger organizations. By leveraging our experience and knowledge from
        working with top tech companies, we aim to level the playing field.
        <br>
        We are committed to providing high-quality, affordable tech solutions that empower small businesses and
        startups to innovate, grow, and succeed in today's competitive market. Our goal is to democratize technology,
        ensuring that everyone has the opportunity to thrive.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

